text: Phryneta immaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hintz in 1911. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Phryneta immaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1911
title: Phryneta immaculata
